Nomura Securities's Matsuzawa Tops Bond-Analyst Ranking by Nikkei Veritas

-- B y   M a s a k i   K o n d o
-- 
2011-04-04T02:54:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/nomura-s-matsuzawa-tops-nikkei-veritas-bond-analyst-ranking-1-.html
Naka Matsuzawa, chief strategist at
Nomura Securities Co. in  Tokyo , was chosen as the top analyst
for Japanese bonds this year in a survey of institutional
investors by Nikkei Veritas.  Hajime Takata, chief strategist at Mizuho Securities Co.,
was ranked second, followed by Jun Ishii, chief fixed-income
strategist at Mitsubishi UFJ Morgan Stanley Securities Co., the
weekly financial newspaper reported yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Masaki Kondo in  Singapore  at 
 mkondo3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rocky Swift at 
 rswift5@bloomberg.net . 